        <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-16">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            艺创AI <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">应用下载</span>
